@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mfntju(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v2 / (0.81 - (tmp + 0.55 / v0 + 0.68)))
    v0 = (tmp * wp.exp((tmp + 0.38 * v1 + 0.70)))
    v1 = wp.cos(((v0 + 0.99 * v2 + 0.13) + wp.abs(v2 + 0.23)))
    tmp = (v0 - (v1 + tmp))
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
